headline: Wynn Resorts’s Q1 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
summary: Wynn Resorts’ first quarter results for 2025 came in below Wall Street’s expectations, with both revenue and adjusted profit missing analyst estimates. Management attributed the year-over-year decline primarily to challenging comparisons given last year’s Super Bowl boost in Las Vegas and lower VIP hold in Macau.
